<body>
     <div class="container">
            <h1 class="header">
                API Basejump: URL Shortener Microservice
            </h1>
            <blockquote>
                User stories:
                <ul>1) I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.</ul>
                <ul>2) I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.</ul>
                <ul>3) I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.</ul>
            </blockquote>
            <h3>Example query usage:</h3>
            <code>https://damp-meadow-51229.herokuapp.com/?url=https://www.freecodecamp.com/</code>
            <h3>Example output:</h3>
            <code>
                {
                  "original_url": "https://www.freecodecamp.com/",
                  "shortened_url": "https://damp-meadow-51229.herokuapp.com/10"
                }
            </code>
            <h3>Example latest output:</h3>
            <code>
                {
                  "original_url": "https://www.freecodecamp.com/",
                  "shortened_url": "https://damp-meadow-51229.herokuapp.com/10"
                }
            </code>
        </div>
</body>
